'''Tijana Jurić''' ({{lang-sr-cyr|Тијана Јурић}}; 4 May 1999<ref name="romanian">{{cite web | url=http://www.copiidisparuti.ro/en/missing-children/278-tijanajuric | title=Tijana Juric | publisher=Romanian Center for Missing & Sexually Exploited Children | date=25 July 2014 | accessdate=21 November 2014}}</ref> — 26 July 2014) was a Serbian girl. She was kidnapped and murdered on 26 July 2014. Dragan Đurić was arrested for the crime.<ref name="dnevnikhr">{{cite web | url=http://dnevnik.hr/vijesti/svijet/pronadjeno-tijelo-nestale-djevojcice-iz-subotice---347018.html | title=Mesar je udario vozilom, uvukao u auto, a potom ubio | publisher=Dnevnik.hr | date=7 August 2014 | accessdate=21 November 2014 |trans-title=Butcher Hit Her With His Car, Took Her In, then Killed Her}}</ref><ref name="jutarnji">{{cite web | url=http://www.jutarnji.hr/jezivi-detalji-monstruoznog-zlocina-ubojica-policiji-u-novom-iskazu-otkrio-sve/1212188/ | title=Jezivi detalji monstruoznog zločina: Ubojica djevojčice Tijane Jurić policiji dao novi iskaz | publisher=[[Jutarnji List]] | date=9 August 2014 | accessdate=21 November 2014 |trans-title=Eerie Details of the Monstrous Crime: Killer of Tijana Juric Gives New Statement to the Police}}</ref><ref name="velj">{{cite web | url=http://www.politika.rs/rubrike/Hronika/Veljovic-Verujem-da-je-Tijana-ziva.sr.html | title=Вељовић: Верујем да је Тијана жива |trans-title=Veljović: I Believe Tijana Is ALive | publisher=[[Politika]] | date=5 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014}}</ref><ref name="rek">{{cite web | url=http://www.blic.rs/Vesti/Hronika/485451/REKONSTRUKCIJA-Tijana-samo-sedam-minuta-bila-sama | title=Tijana samo sedam minuta bila sama | publisher=[[Blic|Blic Online]] | date=5 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Reconstruction: Tijana Was Alone Only for 7 Minutes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rts.rs/page/stories/ci/story/134/%D0%A5%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0/1667061/%D0%A2%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B0+%D0%88%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%9B+%D1%83%D0%B1%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B0,+%D1%83%D1%85%D0%B0%D0%BF%D1%88%D0%B5%D0%BD+%D0%BE%D1%81%D1%83%D0%BC%D1%9A%D0%B8%D1%87%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8+.html | title=Тијана Јурић убијена, ухапшен осумњичени | publisher=[[Radio Television of Serbia|RTS]] | date=7 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Tijana Juric Murdered, Suspect is Arrested}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.subotica.com/vesti/danas-je-dan-zalosti-za-tijanom-id20134.html | title=Danas je Dan žalosti za Tijanom | publisher=Subotica.com | date=8 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Today is a Day of Mourning for Tijana}}</ref><ref name="pat">{{cite web | url=http://www.alo.rs/vesti/hronika/nadena-samo-patika-nestale-devojcice/62451 | title=Nađena samo patika nestale devojčice! | publisher=[[Alo!]] | date=27 July 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Only a Shoe of Missing Girl Found}}</ref><ref name="kur">{{cite web | url=http://www.kurir-info.rs/crna-hronika/tijana-andele-pocivaj-u-miru-sotono-goreces-u-paklu-clanak-1499871 | title=Tijana, anđele, počivaj u miru: Sotono, gorećeš u paklu! | publisher=[[Kurir]] | date=8 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Tijana, Angel, Rest in Peace; Satan, You Will Burn in Hell}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.blic.rs/Vesti/Hronika/486022/Stefanovic-Pokazao-je-gde-je-zakopao-Tijanu-bez-trunke-kajanja | title=Stefanović: Pokazao je gde je zakopao Tijanu, bez trunke kajanja | publisher=[[Blic|Blic Online]] | date=7 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Stefanovic: He Showed the Place Where He Buried Tijana, With No Remorse}}</ref><ref name="anketa">{{cite web | url=http://www.blic.rs/Vesti/Hronika/486134/ANKETA-Da-li-ste-za-vracanje-smrtne-kazne-u-Srbiji | title=Anketa: Da li ste za vraćanje smrtne kazne u Srbiji? | publisher=[[Blic|Blic Online]] | date=7 August 2014 | accessdate=11 August 2014 |trans-title=Opinion Pool: Do You Support Reinstatement of Capital Punis