{{Infobox person | name = Sudha Kaul | image = | imagesize = | caption = | birth_date = | birth_place = India | death_date = | death_place = | restingplace = | restingplacecoordinates = | othername = | occupation = Social worker | yearsactive = | spouse = | domesticpartner = | children = | parents = | influences = | influenced = | website = {{URL||Official web site}} | awards = [[Padma Shri]] }}
'''Sudha Kaul''' is an Indian social worker and educationist, known for her services for the rehabilitation of physically challenged people.<ref name="IICP">{{cite web | url=http://www.iicpindia.org/governingbody.php | title=IICP | publisher=IICP | date=2014 | accessdate=November 17, 2014}}</ref> Dr. Kaul is the vice chairperson of the Indian Institute of [[Cerebral Palsy]] (IICP)<ref name="Cafedissensus">{{cite web | url=http://cafedissensus.com/2013/08/15/an-interview-with-sudha-kaul/ | title=Interview with Dr. Sudha Kaul | publisher=Cafedissensus | work=Video | date=2014 | accessdate=November 17, 2014}}</ref> and the founder Principal of the Centre for Special Education.<ref name="IICP" /> Holder of a doctoral degree in [[Augmentative and Alternative Communication]] (AAC) from [[Manchester Metropolitan University]], Kaul is credited with many books on the subject.<ref name="DINF">{{cite web | url=http://www.dinf.ne.jp/doc/english/asia/resource/apdrj/z13jo0200/z13jo0210.html | title=DINF | publisher=DINF | date=2014 | accessdate=November 17, 2014}}</ref> She has served in many Government committees and held the chair of a government committee formulated to draft new laws for the disabled citizens of India.<ref name="IICP" /> The Government of India honored her in 2010, with the fourth highest civilian award of [[Padma Shri]].<ref name="Padma Shri">{{cite web | url=http://mha.nic.in/sites/upload_files/mha/files/LST-PDAWD-2013.pdf | title=Padma Shri | publisher=Padma Shri | date=2014 | accessdate=November 11, 2014}}</ref> * {{cite web | url=http://www.zoominfo.com/s/#!search/profile/person?personId=48396386&targetid=profile | title=Profile on Zoom Info | publisher=Zoom Info | date=2014 | accessdate=November 17, 2014}}
